      "date": "2013-06-08 06:09:58.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nWhat might also be useful is to change the test-framework to use this data from the import file when needed. For example getting the server build version instead of the current \"do_facet + lctl\" method that doesn't work in some cases, or getting the maximum RPC size of the OST, and similar. \n\nThat could be done in a separate patch, and is version safe, since the updated test-framework code would always be running on a client with the new import data.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
