      "date": "2013-06-11 15:46:06.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/75a922f8-d2aa-11e2-a349-52540035b04c).  Ran 18 tests.  2 tests failed: recovery-small, sanity.",
