      "date": "2013-06-13 11:53:57.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nJohn, you raise a good point.  It might be that Tao already has a patch to convert this code in the upstream linux Git repo, probably worthwhile to take a look before reimplementing it.",
